Case normalization: Convert all tags to lowercase.

Trim whitespace & punctuation: Remove trailing spaces, special characters.

Standardize common synonyms: Map variants to a canonical tag, e.g.:

“rpg”, “role playing”, “role-playing” → “rpg”

“fps”, “first person shooter” → “fps”

Remove or consolidate plurals/singulars: “zombie” vs “zombies”

Fix typos or misspellings (optional with fuzzy matching)

Replace numerals or abbreviations consistently (“2D” vs “two-dimensional”)